---
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Scheduleconsultatioin from '../components/Schedule-consultation.astro'

import '../styles/global.css';
import ScheduleConsultation from '../components/Schedule-consultation.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Creekside marketing pros" 
  description="Grow your buiness by 100%"
>
	<Nav />
    <section class="bg-grey-50 py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <header class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <h2 class="text-primary-900 text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight sm:text-4xl/tight lg:text-5xl/tight">
            Reach and engage your target audience with 
            <span class="text-secondary-500 block">Meta Ads</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-secondary-500 h-1.5 w-20 rounded-full"></div>
        </header>

        <div class="text-grey-700 text-lg/8">
          <p>
            At Creekside Marketing, we've successfully managed over <strong>$20 million in ad spend</strong>, 
            helping businesses of all sizes harness the power of Facebook & Instagram Ads to achieve 
            measurable growth. Our expertise with tools like Meta Pixel enables precise tracking and 
            data-driven optimization, ensuring your ads reach the right audience at the right time. 
            By crafting compelling ad content and employing advanced targeting strategies, we drive 
            engagement, increase website traffic, and boost conversions. Partner with us to transform 
            your social media advertising into a powerful engine for business growth.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
          <img 
            src="/facebook-ads.webp" 
            alt="Team engaging with Facebook Ads on mobile devices" 
            width="1642" 
            height="1100"
            loading="lazy"
            class="h-auto w-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-16 md:py-24" >
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 lg:px-8">

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center rounded-sm border-2 border-secondary-500 bg-white p-10 text-center shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="mb-6 flex size-12 items-center justify-center text-primary-900">
			<img src="/date-range-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="A calander Icon">
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg/none font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-black">
          COMPREHENSIVE META ADS PERFORMANCE ANALYSIS
        </h3>
        <div class="my-6 h-0.5 w-48 bg-secondary-500"></div>
        <p class="text-base/6 font-medium text-grey-900">
        Our insights will guide strategic adjustments to enhance ad performance continually.
      </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center rounded-sm border-2 border-secondary-500 bg-white p-10 text-center shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="mb-6 flex size-12 items-center justify-center text-primary-900">
          <img src="/bar-chart-02-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="A bar chart with accending lines">
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg/none font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-black">
          END-TO-END META ADS CAMPAIGN MANAGEMENT
        </h3>
        <div class="my-6 h-0.5 w-48 bg-secondary-500"></div>
        <p class="text-base/6 font-medium text-grey-900">
        We focus on creating high-quality visuals and compelling ad copy that resonate with your target audience
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center rounded-sm border-2 border-secondary-500 bg-white p-10 text-center shadow-sm transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
        <div class="mb-6 flex size-12 items-center justify-center text-primary-900">
          <img src="/spreadsheet-chart-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="Graphic Spreadsheet with line gragh">
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg/none font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-black">
          ADVANCED CONVERSION TRACKING AND OPTIMIZATION
        </h3>
        <div class="my-6 h-0.5 w-48 bg-secondary-500"></div>
        <p class="text-base/6 font-medium text-grey-900">
        Utilizing tools like Meta Pixel, we meticulously track user interactions stemming from your ads.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
      
      <header>
        <h2 class="text-primary-900 text-4xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight sm:text-5xl/tight lg:text-6xl/tight">
          Unlock the <span class="text-secondary-500">Full Potential</span> of Digital Marketing for Your Business
        </h2>
      </header>

      <div class="text-grey-700 text-lg/8">
        <p>
          Meta Ads offer a wide range of opportunities to connect with your audience and 
          achieve your business goals. From brand awareness to lead generation, we provide expert 
          solutions to engage with potential customers. At Creekside Marketing, we know the ins 
          and outs of Meta's ad ecosystem. Our experts will help you develop targeted ad campaigns, 
          optimize your ad spend, and leverage advanced audience targeting features to ensure 
          maximum ROI. Discover the power of advertising on Meta Sites and witness the impact 
          we can have on your business's growth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid items-center gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="flex justify-center p-4">
        <img 
          src="/meta-ads-sales-target.webp" 
          alt="Illustration of digital marketing targeting" 
          width="1800" 
          height="1200"
          class="h-auto max-w-full"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <img 
          src="/meta-ads-tablet.webp" 
          alt="Analytics dashboard on a digital tablet" 
          width="1800" 
          height="1200"
          class="h-auto max-w-full rounded-sm shadow-sm"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
    <ScheduleConsultation />
    <Footer />
</Layout>